fields.description:
During the middle (quite literally) of a EQL CI run, a test could not create a snapshot because there was no enabled SC:
http://jenkins.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com/job/eutester-test-create-resources/5803/console

After looking at the logs:
http://jenkins.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com/job/eutester-test-gather-logs/5362/artifact/*zip*/archive.zip
